# Senior Living Market Size & Share | Industry Report, 2033
## Report Summary
The global senior living market size was estimated at USD 2.02 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 3.25 billion by 2033, growing at a CAGR of 5.48% from 2025 to 2033.

## Key Market Trends & Insights
* North America led the global market in 2024, with the largest revenue share of 60.40%.
* The U.S. senior living industry is anticipated to register the fastest CAGR from 2025 to 2033.
* By facility, the active adults 55+ community segment held the largest revenue share of 69.52% in 2024.

## Market Size & Forecast
* 2024 Market Size: USD 2.02 Billion
* 2033 Projected Market Size: USD 3.25 Billion
* CAGR (2025-2033): 5.48%
* North America: Largest Market in 2024
* Asia Pacific: Fastest growing market

## Aging Population & Increasing Life Expectancy
The rapid rise in the aging population and rising life expectancy are primarily driving the expansion of the senior living market. 
