## Recent Developments
* Solera Senior Living introduced a pioneering multi-partner care model at its Lumina Las Vegas Memory Care community.
* Vedaanta Senior Living introduced Vyom360, an in-house technology platform designed to enhance the quality of care, streamline daily services, and improve resident engagement.
* Inspiren launched the first complete AI-driven senior living ecosystem, aiming to transform the senior care industry by integrating advanced technology with compassionate care.

